IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SampleApp.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  NUM1          PIC 9(5) VALUE 100.
01  NUM2          PIC 9(5) VALUE 200.
01  SUM           PIC 9(5).
01  DIFFERENCE    PIC 9(5).
01  PRODUCT       PIC 9(10).
01  QUOTIENT      PIC 9(5)V99.
01  WS-DATE       PIC X(10).
01  WS-TIME       PIC X(8).
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    COMPUTE SUM = NUM1 + NUM2.
    COMPUTE DIFFERENCE = NUM2 - NUM1.
    COMPUTE PRODUCT = NUM1 * NUM2.
    COMPUTE QUOTIENT = NUM2 / NUM1.
    MOVE FUNCTION CURRENT-DATE TO WS-DATE.
    MOVE FUNCTION CURRENT-TIME TO WS-TIME.
    DISPLAY 'Sum: ' SUM.
    DISPLAY 'Difference: ' DIFFERENCE.
    DISPLAY 'Product: ' PRODUCT.
    DISPLAY 'Quotient: ' QUOTIENT.
    DISPLAY 'Date: ' WS-DATE.
    DISPLAY 'Time: ' WS-TIME.
    STOP RUN.
